data.description: Welcome to this beautiful pool home located in the Estate section of Town Park with great curb appeal and lush landscaping all around! This spacious Newport Model built by Johnson Group has over 2,200 sq. ft of living area, and volume ceilings that gives you that grand feeling throughout!  As soon as you enter, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light and tile floors that seamlessly flow throughout the entire home. Rest assured knowing that this home comes equipped with a new roof (2021), A/C (2021) and water heater (2023). Plus, the front windows have been replaced in 2018 and hurricane shutter for added for a peace of mind.  The kitchen offers white cabinetry, stainless appliances, plenty of storage, breakfast bar and and eat-in-kitchen that overlooks the lanai and living room .The owner's suite has a trey ceiling, 2 walk-in closets one is a safe room, double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, water closet, and sliders that lead out to the covered lanai and pool. Enjoy the fully fenced backyard & covered lanai area. The sparkling pool is an inviting oasis, providing a refreshing escape during hot summer days. Centrally located just a few miles to the Pavilion at Port Orange shops, restaurants, beach, and I-95 & I-4.
